    <條號>Article 9</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The positions and its prescribed vacancies compiled within this regulation are listed in the tables below.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 10</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[After this regulation being amended and executed on Dec. 29, 2006, the MPS cannot hire civilian employees, but the ones those who have been hired can may be employed until till their demission.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 11</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This regulation takes effect upon the date of officielization.
]]></條文內容>
